GET /search
Search a state's nursing board by name. Returns matching license records you then resolve down with /verify. Use this when you do not have a license number in hand. Some states (notably NY) do not return status or expiration on search alone. California requires up to 3 CAPTCHA solves per search and can take 15 to 70 seconds.
